    <item>
      <title>针对Credit S债券损失对三菱摩根提起第三起诉讼——索赔金额达83亿日元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/-83</link>
      <description><![CDATA[14名个人投资者对三菱日联摩根士丹利证券提起集体诉讼，该公司出售了瑞士信贷集团的永久次级债券（AT1债券），该债券已变得一文不值。据悉，28日又提起新诉讼。受此影响，索赔总额增至约83亿日元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/-83</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 05:23:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三菱日联金融集团子公司因瑞士信贷 AT1 损失在日本再次遭起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/mufg-s-unit-sued-again-in-japan-for-credit-suisse-at1-losses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士信贷向客户出售的风险最高的债券变得毫无价值，一年多以来，日本越来越多的投资者对三菱日联金融集团旗下的经纪部门提起了诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/mufg-s-unit-sued-again-in-japan-for-credit-suisse-at1-losses</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 05:21:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>干预赌注增加，日元兑美元汇率跌至 161 下方</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/yen-falls-through-161-per-dollar-as-intervention-wagers-increase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美元普遍走强的背景下，日元兑美元汇率周五跌至 161 关口，为 1986 年以来首次，这引发了日本干预市场的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/yen-falls-through-161-per-dollar-as-intervention-wagers-increase</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 02:07:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本东证指数创 1990 年以来最高盘中水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/japan-s-benchmark-topix-stock-index-is-heading-for-1990-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本东证指数周五触及 1990 年以来的最高水平，随后回吐了部分涨幅，由于提高股东回报的努力以及受益于更高利率的金融股，该股指获得了支撑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/japan-s-benchmark-topix-stock-index-is-heading-for-1990-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 00:17:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
